==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Morion
<hw>Mo"ri*on</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[F.
<ets>morion</ets>, Sp. <ets>morrion</ets>; cf. Sp. <ets>morra</ets> the
upper part of the head, <ets>morro</ets> anything that is round.]</ety>
<def>A kind of open helmet, without visor or beaver, and somewhat
resembling a hat.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>A battered <qex>morion</qex> on his brow.</q> <rj><qau>Sir W.
Scott.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Morion</ent>⟦br⟧

